ffoorrttuunnee -- Command

Print randomly selected, hopefully humorous, text
/uussrr/ggaammeess/ffoorrttuunnee [ _f_i_l_e ]

ffoorrttuunnee prints a  message that is randomly selected from  the contents of a
text  file.   ffoorrttuunnee reads  _f_i_l_e  if  it is  named  on  the command  line;
otherwise, it reads the default file /uussrr/ggaammeess/lliibb/ffoorrttuunneess.

_F_i_l_e_s
