ccoommmmaannddss

_N_o_t_e_s
The fortunes  included in  /uussrr/ggaammeess/lliibb/ffoorrttuunneess were selected  mainly on
the grounds that  they would not give offense to  anyone.  We encourage you
to update this file with your own favorite witticisms.
